\ls1\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 we focus on the goals of learning rather than valuing for itself\
\ls1\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs24 edification \'97 instruction for intellectual improvement\
\ls1\ilvl1
\f2\fs20 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
